prggmr is a high-performance event processing engine, it uses Events, Signals,
Subscriptions, Queues and an Engine, that have been engineered from the ground
up to be incredibly lightweight, fast, efficent and robust with simplicity and
ease of use in mind.

prggmr is much more than an event library, it is a robust standalone event
processing engine written in PHP, allowing for application &amp; server level
php programming as if it wasn't even php.

Read More @ http://www.prggmr.org